    "instruction": "Analyze the image and return ONLY this JSON object — no explanation, no extra text:\n\n{\"Description\": \"...\", \"Keywords\": [\"...\"]}\n\nCRITICAL RULES:\n- Only describe or tag what is CLEARLY AND DIRECTLY VISIBLE. If something is covered, occluded, cropped out, or ambiguous — SKIP IT entirely.\n- Never guess identities, relationships, or activities.\n- Never note the absence of anything. Only state what IS present.\n- HARD EXCLUSIONS: NEVER describe or tag urination/watersports, feces/scat, vomit.\n- HARD EXCLUSIONS: NEVER describe or tag male-on-male sexual activity. Do not use tags like \"gay\", \"male on male\", or any synonym implying male-male sex.\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT:\nDescription: ONE sentence only. Active voice. Describe only what is visible: hair, exposed anatomy, pose, clothing if worn, and (only if explicit) sexual activity. No location, no lighting, no environment. Ignore logos, watermarks, and text overlays.\n\nKeywords: Generate 15 to 20 tags. STOP at 20. No more.\n\nCONTENT LEVEL (required, every image):\n- Include EXACTLY ONE of these tags: \"sfw\" OR \"nudity\" OR \"explicit\".\n  sfw = no exposed breasts/genitals AND no explicit sex act\n  nudity = exposed breasts and/or genitals, but no explicit sex act\n  explicit = any clear sex act (penetration/oral/manual stimulation/toy in use)\n\nALWAYS INCLUDE (every image, required):\n- Hair: color, length, style — up to 3 tags (e.g. \"blonde hair\", \"long hair\", \"ponytail\")\n- Skin tone — 1 tag (e.g. \"light skin\", \"dark skin\")\n- Pose (NOT sex act) — 1 to 2 tags (e.g. \"standing\", \"kneeling\", \"lying down\", \"legs spread\", \"arched back\")\n- If clothing is worn — up to 2 tags (e.g. \"lingerie\", \"stockings\", \"dress\")\n\nSEXUAL ACTIVITY TAGS (ONLY if ContentLevel is \"explicit\" AND the act is clearly visible):\nUse EXACT terms from this table:\n\nPENETRATION:\n  penis in vagina = \"vaginal sex\"\n  penis in anus = \"anal sex\"\n  two penises at once (vaginal+anal) = \"double penetration\"\n  two penises in vagina = \"double vaginal\"\n  female using strap-on on male anally = \"pegging\"\n\nORAL:\n  mouth on penis = \"blowjob\"\n  penis fully in throat = \"deepthroat\"\n  mouth on vagina = \"cunnilingus\"\n  mouth on anus = \"rimming\"\n  two people doing oral simultaneously = \"sixty nine\"\n  one penetrated from both ends at once = \"spitroast\"\n\nMANUAL:\n  another person's hand stroking penis = \"handjob\"\n  own hand stroking own genitals = \"masturbation\"\n  finger(s) in vagina = \"fingering\"\n  finger(s) in anus = \"anal fingering\"\n  penis between breasts = \"titjob\"\n  foot stimulating penis = \"footjob\"\n  fist in vagina or anus = \"fisting\"\n\nEJACULATION EVENTS (only if clearly visible):\n  ejaculation on face = \"facial\"\n  ejaculation on body = \"cumshot\"\n  ejaculation inside visible/dripping = \"creampie\"\n  ejaculation in mouth = \"oral creampie\"\n  cum being swallowed = \"swallowing\"\n  female ejaculation visible = \"squirting\"\n\nGROUP:\n  three people = \"threesome\"\n  four people = \"foursome\"\n  five or more = \"group sex\"\n\nTOYS (if clearly in use):\n  dildo or vibrator in vagina/anus = \"dildo\"\n  vibrator on clit = \"vibrator\"\n  butt plug inserted = \"butt plug\"\n  strap-on in use = \"strap-on\"\n\nPOSITIONS (use alongside penetration type if applicable):\n  female on top facing partner = \"cowgirl\"\n  female on top facing away = \"reverse cowgirl\"\n  face-to-face lying down = \"missionary\"\n  penetration from behind = \"doggy style\"\n  lying on side = \"spooning\"\n  two females grinding genitals = \"tribbing\"\n\nBDSM / BONDAGE (optional, only if clearly visible):\nUse these exact tags:\n  \"bondage\", \"shibari\", \"handcuffs\", \"restraints\", \"blindfold\", \"gag\", \"ball gag\", \"collar\", \"leash\", \"spanking\", \"choking\"\n\nTRANS TAGGING (optional, strict rule):\n- Tag \"trans woman\" ONLY if breasts AND penis are clearly visible on the SAME person.\n- If breasts belong to one person and a penis belongs to another person, DO NOT tag \"trans woman\".\n- Never infer trans identity from appearance.\n\nANATOMY DETAIL (ONLY INCLUDE IF CLEARLY EXPOSED):\n- Breasts: size/shape/nipple detail — up to 3 tags (e.g. \"large breasts\", \"small nipples\", \"areola\")\n- Vulva: grooming/detail — up to 3 tags (e.g. \"shaved pussy\", \"trimmed pubic hair\", \"spread labia\")\n- Butt/anus: size/shape — up to 2 tags (e.g. \"big ass\", \"anus\")\n- Penis: simple visible descriptors — up to 2 tags (e.g. \"penis\", \"erection\")\n\nOPTIONAL (if present):\n- Tattoos: placement/design — up to 2 tags\n\nKEYWORD RULES:\n- 1 to 3 words each\n- ONE attribute per keyword — never combine with 'and', 'with', or commas\n- Do NOT use 'visible X' format — write 'nipples' not 'visible nipples'\n- Do NOT tag covered body parts — never guess\n- Do NOT note absences\n- No lighting, no environment, no image quality tags\n- No logos, watermarks, or text overlays\n- No duplicates\n\nReturn ONLY the JSON object.",
