ags (write \"shoes\" not \"black shoes\"). Exception: hair color, skin tone, and nipple color tags always keep their color\n- Nail tags: output only \"nails\" or \"nail polish\" — never include color (correct: \"nails\"; wrong: \"blue nails\", \"dark nails\", \"painted nails\")\n- No duplicates\n- NEVER output negative or absence keywords. If an attribute is absent or not mentioned, skip that step — never write \"no X\", \"not X\", or \"without X\"\n- Output only the JSON array, nothing else",
